STATE of Louisiana
v.
Edmond D. SPENCER NO. 2018-KH-1230 Supreme Court of Louisiana. September 28, 2018

WRIT NOT CONSIDERED. Petitioner has not demonstrated that he sought review in the court(s) below before filing in *148this Court nor shown the "extraordinary circumstances" that would justify bypassing that level of review. La.S.Ct.R. X § 5(b).
